ocr-interpreted-text.ocr-interpreted-line: Other leading members are: Sir Henry Lintott from the Commonwealth Relations
Ofﬁce, Sir William Corell—Barnes (Colonial Oﬁ'ice), Mr. G. R. Bell (Treasury), and Mr.
